<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-09-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-02-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="391" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d391">
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                                </head>
                                <p>The Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_842">p.
                                        842</ref>, records that Roosevelt dined with the Churchill
                                    family and Hopkins, and that Roosevelt and Churchill were
                                    closeted for several hours following dinner. No record of the
                                    discussion during or after dinner has been found.</p>
                            </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>